               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17570713-4-off18-c39" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570713-4-defend44 t17570713-4-off18 t17570713-4-verdict22"></join>
         
               <p>247. (M.) 
               
                  <persName id="t17570713-4-defend44" type="defendantName">
                     Mary 
                     Sellars 
                  <interp inst="t17570713-4-defend44" type="surname" value="Sellars"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570713-4-defend44" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570713-4-defend44" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , <rs id="t17570713-4-deflabel17" type="occupation">widow</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570713-4-defend44 t17570713-4-deflabel17"></join>, was indicted for <rs id="t17570713-4-off18" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17570713-4-off18" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570713-4-off18" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing 4 s. 6 d. in money numbered
            </rs>, the money of 
               
                  <persName id="t17570713-4-victim46" type="victimName">
                     Ann 
                     Pool 
                  <interp inst="t17570713-4-victim46" type="surname" value="Pool"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570713-4-victim46" type="given" value="Ann"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570713-4-victim46" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570713-4-off18 t17570713-4-victim46"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17570713-4-viclabel19" type="occupation">widow</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570713-4-victim46 t17570713-4-viclabel19"></join>, <rs id="t17570713-4-cd20" type="crimeDate">May 27</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570713-4-off18 t17570713-4-cd20"></join>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17570713-4-person47">
                  Ann 
                  Pool 
               <interp inst="t17570713-4-person47" type="surname" value="Pool"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570713-4-person47" type="given" value="Ann"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570713-4-person47" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live in <placeName id="t17570713-4-crimeloc21">Christopher's Alley, Moorfields</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17570713-4-crimeloc21" type="placeName" value="Christopher's Alley, Moorfields"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17570713-4-crimeloc21" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570713-4-off18 t17570713-4-crimeloc21"></join>. On the 27th of May I had 4 s. 6 d. taken out of my cupboard. I took up the prisoner, and before the justice she own'd she took it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17570713-4-person48">
                  Robert 
                  Moody 
               <interp inst="t17570713-4-person48" type="surname" value="Moody"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570713-4-person48" type="given" value="Robert"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570713-4-person48" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner was taken up for this offence. I saw her fall on her knees, and acknowledge she took the money mentioned, and she returned some of it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I don't know what I said, I was so affrighted. <rs id="t17570713-4-verdict22" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17570713-4-verdict22" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17570713-4-punish23" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17570713-4-punish23" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17570713-4-punish23" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="branding"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17570713-4-defend44 t17570713-4-punish23"></join>
               
                     <note>[Branding. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
            </div1>
